body.transcript:
Hello! Thank you for calling Harmony Music School. My name is Keith Sanchez. May I know your name, please?

Hi Keith, I’m Jennifer Smith.

Nice to meet you, Jennifer. How can I assist you today?

I’m quite surprised! I recently returned a music book, but I haven't received a confirmation email. Can you help me with that?

Of course, I can help with that. Could you please provide me with the order number of your return?

Yes, the order number is M-S five six seven eight.

Thank you, Jennifer. Can I also have the last four digits of the card you used for the purchase?

It's one two three four.

Thank you for the information. I see that the return was processed on our end and you should receive a confirmation email shortly.

Oh, that’s a relief! Thank you so much for your help, Keith.

You're welcome, Jennifer. Thank you for your patience and for choosing Harmony Music School. Have a great day!
